01:01:14.754 --> 01:01:16.839
<i>Ang isang ordinaryong tanawin</i>
<i>sa buhay natin</i>

01:01:18.841 --> 01:01:21.302
<i>maaaring maging di-malilimutang liwanag</i>

01:01:22.470 --> 01:01:23.680
<i>na magdadala sa inyo sa kung saan,</i>

01:01:26.057 --> 01:01:27.266
<i>sa kung anong paraan,</i>

01:01:28.476 --> 01:01:30.645
<i>at kung kanino man.</i>

01:01:34.691 --> 01:01:36.067
<i>Sana ang araw na ito</i>

01:01:36.150 --> 01:01:38.778
<i>ay isa uling makabuluhang araw</i>

01:01:39.487 --> 01:01:41.948
<i>kung kailan sinundan n'yo</i>
<i>ang nagniningning na liwanag.</i>

01:01:43.658 --> 01:01:44.701
<i>Magaling,</i>

01:01:46.369 --> 01:01:47.954
<i>nalagpasan n'yo ang araw na ito.</i>

01:01:53.668 --> 01:01:55.420
Ang susunod na station…

